reviews.text: Great location, offers phone with hotspot, and nice dining area beautiful hotel overall

Had tea buffet here. Enjoy 20% off for credit card offer. (Around $300 per person) magnificent dining environment, Decent food and great waiter service. Certainly a place to chill out with friends and family.
Love this hotel. Greatest return on your dollar. The 17th floor with top notch Gym swimming pool and spa is the highlight.
Good, clean and modern hotel with a great location.

Classic Value for Money choice

We love this hotel especially the restaurants and new building skytower and lounge right below it. 

The hotel was build dated back in 80s/90s so ceiling is not high on most floor but the halo space between each hotel floors and it cafe is one of the best and remains architecture you can only find here (as new fire rule apply)

There are plenty of above 5 stars hotels in town, but this is one of the value for money choice

reviews.text:
If you’re looking for a luxury hotel this is it. Great location. Excellent amenities. Exceptional service from all staff. 
Experience the sky club and you won’t regret it. We Would definitely come back here again. 
Thank you 👍🏽

Fancy hotel with excellent service, amenities and location. The lobby has some stores like Rolex. They also have different restaurants with several cuisines. Well decorated place inside and outside the room. The bath is spacious and very clean. The unique service is the free handy cell phone that can call, text and connect to the internet with hot spot option. They also provide free water to support plastic-free initiative.

A very nice hotel located in the middle of Tsimshtsui East area managed by Sun Hung Kai Group. Location is excellent and the hotel is well managed despite its establishment more than 30 years ago. The Italian, Japanese and Vietnamese restaurants are worth a try. Rooms are clean and tidy and the staff are helpful.

Main thing for me was aroma/smell in the hotel. Amazing! Starting from reception zone - ending my room. They did special aroma in every corner. Also there is a gym with swimming pool and spa. Love it a lot. And breakfasts were also in Asian and European style.

Nice room, staff all very friendly and helpful. Room service food was pretty good and the breakfast buffet was the same high standard you would expect from a hotel like this. I have stayed there twice for work a would stay there again.

가성비가 좋은 곳이고, 나름대로 관리가 잘 되는 곳으로 ICON이 너무 비싼 분은 여기도 생각해보시면 좋을 것 같습니다. 단 view는 기대하시면 안되고, view가 중요하시면 바로 옆의 inter-continental stanford로 가시는게 맞을 것 같습니다(가격은 비슷합니다). 전 view에 크게 신경을 쓰지 않는 경향이고 그보다는 침대 시트나 청소 등 청결도나 관리가 더 중요한데 그 부분은 잘 관리되는 곳이라고 느껴져서 매우 만족하면서 묵었습니다. 침사추이 중심가(역/하버시티)와는 약간 거리가 있지만 promenade쪽으로 나가서 바다 보면서 좀 걷다보면 생각보다 금새 갑니다.

去帝苑開會，帝苑有無敵大海景，房間很大，服務贊！基本上問任何一何員工，都很清楚我要去開會的客人，不會問長問短，太好啦。
最喜歡就是中庭，坐在玻璃電梯內，很有氣派，還可以看到在地面用餐的客人，和漂亮噴泉。

reviews.text:
콘스프가 엄떠서 아슈워떠혀.
기뵨으로 콘스프가 있능거 아닝가효?
연어는 죨라 크고 😍 죨라 쨔요. 구치만 머글만해효.
리뷰가 죠턴데 유일하게 마시께 머근건 바나나.
아메리카노
海鮮為主的自助晚餐，環境優雅舒適，氣氛不俗，晚間有樂手表演，枱與枱之間嘅位置比較狹窄，食物頗豐富，甜品也不少，水果都算多，整體都唔錯。
現場有live，很放鬆，生日送的蛋糕很滑，拿破崙餅的騷皮超好吃，地方很大，送的鮑魚很鬆軟
優雅的餐飲場所,晚間有樂手表演,我女兒生日點唱三首歌,都唱了,還喊了女兒名字,大家都很開心
